<item>
            <title>[RAT-344] Rat report contains multiple output runs instead of only one</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/RAT-344</link>
                <project id="12310750" key="RAT">Apache RAT</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Comparing projects that use RAT in v0.15 and v0.16 I realized that in v0.16 target/rat.txt contains multiple outputs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In RAT 0.15 only one output was generated, while in 0.16 it seems as if multiple RAT runs are written in one file each after the other.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How2reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Compare target/rat.txt in a project running v0.15 and apply v0.16 in the same project&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Executed maven goal: mvn apache-rat:check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
